text:
Hey hey ......
Bhai agar tu nhi hota, toh koi trip ke plans successful ho hi nahi paate. Ho bhi jaate, par maza nahi aata. First year me tune CCD leja leja ke pagal kar dia tha… aur Kanpur ke saare restaurants me le gaya tu….. Yaar itni energy kissi me nhi hoti, tu pehla aadmi tha jo itni saari jagah ghumne le gaya. Har din tera rona laga rahta tha yaha chalo kabhi wahan chalo….. College me kitni masti ki yaar tere saath, sab bhai baith ke kya bulla kaathe the. Aur woh tune bong maar ke BT me chala gaya, aisi gaand fati thi teri xD.. Aur woh e-rickshaw wala scene…. Yaar yeh baatein toh hamesha yaad rahegi. 

Tune sabko humesha sabhi bhaiyon ko khush aur jod ke rakha he…. Bohot dil saaf hai tera. Tune hamesha mujhe sagha bhai mana he. Tere saath sari bakchodiyan ki he college me. Har waqt call lagta, pagal kar deta. Itna koi nahi call lagake puchta mere liye, jitna tu karta. Bye ka toh koi sense hi nahi tujhe, kyunki phirse call aayega tera “Kya kar raha he?”.  Thanks for being all the way with me.

text:
